  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault] --> Idle: File Opened (HealthTech_PatientRecords)\n\n    state \"User Edits File\" as UserAction\n    Idle --> UserAction: User types a character\n\n    state \"Request Lock\" as RequestLock {HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\n        }\n    }\n\n    GrantLock --> LockedState: 200 OK\n    DenyLock --> ConflictState: 409 Conflict\n\n    state \"Locked (HealthTech_PatientRecords)\" as LockedState {HealthTech_PatientRecords] --> Editing\n        Editing --> Heartbeat: Every 30s\n        Heartbeat --> ServerUpdate: UPDATE locks SET timestamp\n        ServerUpdate --> Editing: 200 OK\n        \n        Editing --> Unlock: User saves/closes/stops\n    }\n\n    state \"Conflict (HealthTech_PatientRecords)\" as ConflictState {HealthTech_PatientRecords] --> ShowWarning: Display \"File Locked by User B\"\n        ShowWarning --> Idle: User cancels edit\n    }\n\n    Unlock --> Idle: DELETE /lock (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\n    \n    note right of Heartbeat\n        Prevents \"Stale Locks\" if\n        PC crashes or loses power.\n    end note",
