  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，描述HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault里PatientRecords文件的协作编辑流程。核心问题是处理多用户同时编辑时的锁机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "lockedstate",
        "conflictstate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，HIPAA合规的EMR系统。我先确认一下起点：文件从Vault打开后，初始状态是Idle？然后用户开始编辑才触发锁请求？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "UserAction",
        "RequestLock"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Idle是文件刚打开的状态。用户敲第一个字符就进入UserAction状态，这时候系统要向HealthTech_EMR_Sync请求锁。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "UserAction",
        "RequestLock",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我画好了Idle到UserAction的转换，标注\"User types a character\"。现在处理锁请求的分支：GrantLock和DenyLock两种情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "UserAction",
        "GrantLock",
        "DenyLock"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GrantLock成功的话进入LockedState，这是核心编辑状态。但这里有个细节——DeniedLock不能直接结束，要进入ConflictState给用户提示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GrantLock",
        "LockedState",
        "DenyLock",
        "ConflictState"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "ConflictState的具体行为是什么？用户看到冲突后只能取消吗，还是可以强制覆盖？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConflictState",
        "ShowWarning",
        "Idle"
